
to build it:
    make firehalo

to run it:
    mpirun -n 16 ./firehalo 1600


Please read the code and try to understand what it is doing.

LoR -- left or right
ToB -- top or bottom
LHS -- left hand side
RHS -- right hand side

The halo exchange is done in the halosendreceive.c "library".
The main body sets up everything but you need to add the
"compute next generation" part.

